8:15:10.000Z","msg":"黑警最識玩語言偽術<br />\n水樽係<span style=\"color: red;\">「攻擊性武器」</span><br />\n哮喘藥係<span style=\"color: red;\">「第一部毒藥」</span><br />\n<br />\n但自己釋放毒氣，就叫做<span style=\"color: red;\">「煙」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">煙你老母？</span></span>"},{"pid":"6c36f69a690b415102d10ec70eb15f7519eaf8c6","tid":1375903,"uid":265987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:16:12.000Z","msg":"wish"},{"pid":"391d31f987850825113bc1596bbf383912d347a2","tid":1375903,"uid":265987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c36f69a690b415102d10ec70eb15f7519eaf8c6","tid":1375903,"uid":265987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:16:12.000Z","msg":"wish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fb82e8ef3a009c76793d39f46104f73ce49e76","tid":1375903,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"59c757839f742dae0b202966c72cb9a42716acf1","tid":1375903,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14f385b7da61fceba85adc6238de34689153e47","tid":1375903,"uid":16278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:20:03.000Z","msg":"2014年已經有人屌「催淚煙」係語言藝術<br />\n<a href=\"http://aukalun.blogspot.com/2014/09/blog-post_30.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faukalun.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F09%2Fblog-post_30.html&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpz2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=ee1305e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://aukalun.blogspot.com/2014/09/blog-post_30.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">//警察不叫「催淚彈」，叫「催淚煙」，多麼輕柔，多麼文藝，語言偽術甚深境界。//</span>"},{"pid":"1d5451dfa6a0371cbe2aaf018c280dada76969ff","tid":1375903,"uid":16278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpz2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=70e9cb04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88</a><br />\n<br />\n催淚彈若在室內使用，催淚氣體將無法散去，導致示威者（甚至其他市民）窒息死亡。<br />\n<br />\n當無防護人員在近距離被催淚彈命中、直接暴露於高濃度毒劑或長時間暴露於低濃度毒劑中時，可能將因角膜受損而永久失去視覺能力。"},{"pid":"12429922bb501e0a7ea53c9bfde42c760718ed00","tid":1375903,"uid":92353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:47:47.000Z","msg":"仲要成日用&quot;施放&quot;  個term 勁溫和"},{"pid":"05d364538c5a407d86f6d09ae7ab1d953c7dcca4","tid":1375903,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"為毒氣正名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5446403c30a04d9af3c65696b40851479d099b8f","tid":1375903,"uid":251477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:51:41.000Z","msg":"務必置頂！預備運動最後全面升級，聯結國內，引發全國茉莉花革命！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1375948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1375948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea64c800f6b5ab988961eaa01fa21d1553a1549b","tid":1375903,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FX62ts8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFX62ts8.jpg&h=54fa1f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民頭盔 可以<br />\n1)每人一物資, 唔怕比人充公<br />\n2)有noise<br />\n3)比狗逗可以串番佢 [就係警察保護唔到市民,我地先要自己保護自己, 仲好意思問戴頭盔做咩, 知